[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl021_01",
        "zh_CN": "权限认证通过，供能已经恢复。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl021_02",
        "zh_CN": "再等几分钟，大货梯就能启动了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "辛苦你了，奈莉德……还有优格。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl021_03",
        "zh_CN": "没什么，现在我能做到的也就只有这些了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与奈莉德汇合后，我们找到了一处污染较轻的房间作为新的临时据点。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "优格",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_npc084_01",
        "zh_CN": "呼……呼……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一旁的优格静静地躺在那里，仿佛只是陷入了深深的睡眠。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl021_04",
        "zh_CN": "……屋里有点闷，我出去透透气。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl021_05",
        "zh_CN": "一会儿电梯启动了，我再回来通知你们。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在留下了一个意味深长的眼神后，奈莉德便拿起终端走向门外。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "门在她身后轻轻合上，房间里顿时安静得只剩下我与妮塔的呼吸声。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她背靠着墙，低着头，拳头攥得微微发白，平日里那股乐观开朗的气势此刻早已消失得无影无踪。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还在自责吗？这可不像是平时的你啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我起身走到她的身边，然后学着她的样子，靠在了墙上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_01",
        "zh_CN": "平时的我……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，平时的妮塔无论遇到什么挫折都会马上打起精神吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_02",
        "zh_CN": "啊，那倒也是……毕竟我的“人设”就是这样的嘛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_03",
        "zh_CN": "开朗直爽，无论遇到什么困难都不会被轻易打败。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_04",
        "zh_CN": "跌倒了，只要再爬起来就好……一直以来，未曾改变。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以啊，我才说只有“平时的你”才是这样的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我打断了她那有些自嘲般的叙述。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_05",
        "zh_CN": "哎？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我可不是让妮塔去硬着头皮装作一切都无所谓的样子。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "现在的妮塔，一定是遇到了无法靠自己解决的问题了吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_06",
        "zh_CN": "嗯……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而且你认定这个问题会给我造成麻烦，所以便一直回避着去面对它。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "老实说，我很受伤。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_07",
        "zh_CN": "唔……别这么说嘛，我知道错了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "既然如此，那就不妨和我说说到底是怎么一回儿事？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_08",
        "zh_CN": "……那你得保证，不许再为了我，做出伤害自己的行为了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我保证。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_09",
        "zh_CN": "……哈。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_10",
        "zh_CN": "说到底，其实还是我神格本身的问题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_11",
        "zh_CN": "在接受神格神经的那一天，我就发现了，那其中蕴含着一股庞大而又狂暴的能量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_12",
        "zh_CN": "“把一切都破坏掉吧，把一切付之一炬吧。”",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_13",
        "zh_CN": "每当我将手伸向那股能量时，总会下意识地听到类似的声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但是妮塔并没有被蛊惑，并没有输给那个声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_14",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，是的，不过可能和分析员想象中的不太一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_15",
        "zh_CN": "我并不是没有输给那个声音，而是，我根本就没有勇气去挑战它……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_16",
        "zh_CN": "那股力量，在我内心中，具化成一堵硕大的火墙。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_17",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你应该还记得我之前和你说过的孤儿院的故事吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_18",
        "zh_CN": "以前，嗯……这么说吧，我呢，不知道自己父母的样子跟声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_19",
        "zh_CN": "从记事起孤儿院就是我的家，我的家人自然也是孤儿院的老师跟孩子们。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_20",
        "zh_CN": "再后来……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_21",
        "zh_CN": "再后来的故事，是因为一场恶意纵火事故，那所孤儿院被烧成了灰烬。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的眉头微微颤抖，即便已经过去很久了，但这件事却依旧将她束缚在某处。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_22",
        "zh_CN": "这件事，既是我下定决心要变强的起点，也是我一直无法面对的梦魇。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "并非无法面对，训练测试的时候，一切都很正常不是吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我继续用温柔的言语，鼓励着说出心事的她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_23",
        "zh_CN": "那是因为那仅仅是“训练”，一旦到实战中就不一样了，稍有疏忽，很有可能就会彻底失控。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_24",
        "zh_CN": "我很清楚，自己并没有那么强大，也不该那么盲目自信……但即便如此……即便如此啊……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_25",
        "zh_CN": "我也不能，就这样眼睁睁地看着自己最喜欢的人，因为自己的胆怯而受伤！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_26",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "将情感全部宣泄出来的她，在深吸一口气后，又将头深深地低了下去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_27",
        "zh_CN": "但哪怕有了悸响的加持，哪怕我拼尽全力地训练，我也还是没有办法驾驭那样庞大的能量……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_28",
        "zh_CN": "那时……我的力量不光失去了控制，还烧伤了为我操心的分析员……这样的我实在是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔，烧伤我的人，并不是你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我握住了她的手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_29",
        "zh_CN": "哎？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你忘了吗，当时你的火焰融化了建筑，融化了泰坦……但却唯独，没有伤害到我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_30",
        "zh_CN": "可是分析员的手臂和胸口……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那些都是吸收过量泰坦物质后的正常反应，不是妮塔的错。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_31",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一声短暂的哽咽后，妮塔抬起了头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当然，如果妮塔实在担心的话，下次我不会再这么做了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep7_girl003_32",
        "zh_CN": "下次……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，我说过了吧，我相信妮塔，无论什么样的力量，你一定都能搞得定的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我之所以会做出这个判断，那是因为你曾经和我说过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
